Are you a Perks cardholder? Download the Perks mobile app for free today to make the most of your Perks card by continuously saving on the go. Login for instant access to all your EXCLUSIVE discounts of up to 50% off at various hotels, restaurants, cafés, golf courses, bowling alleys, gyms, leisure centres, high street shops, hairdressers, cinemas and much more across the country!

As one of the leading employee rewards programmes across the UK and Ireland, Perks brings over 1,500 substantial savings to your fingertips with something for everyone to enjoy from all your local favourites to big, nationwide brands.

With the Perks app, you can:
• Search for specific offers with ease by keyword or location using the search bar.
• Browse our 7 categories to find deals tailored to you.
• Use the map function to find the nearby discounts on your doorstep, or look for offers in a different town by simply adjusting the map or by typing the location in the search bar.
• Leave reviews on any offers you have redeemed to share your experience with other Perks members.
• Save your favourite offers for later, enabling you to save time and time again!
• Suggest venues to us for possible discounts in the near future…

And redeeming an offer on the app is simple:
• Choose your favourite(s) offer from the 1,500 available
• Press the ‘How to Use’ button on the full offer page and follow the redemption instructions 
• Visit the venue to avail of your offer, and enjoy!

Take the tour to best familiarize yourself with how the app works, and be sure to visit regularly to enter exciting competitions and ensure you don’t miss out on the newest offers!

“I love the app. It’s very handy when you’re in a new town and you would like to see what offers are close”

Please note: You must have a valid Perks Card in order to register and/or login on the app.

We’re here to help! Got a question, suggestion or need help accessing the app? please Contact Us at info@perksdirectory.com

THE UK’S HAIR & BEAUTY BOOKING APP

Over 2 million appointments booked monthly. 63,000+ salons on board. Treatwell is the fastest, easiest, and most-loved way to book hair, beauty, massage, health, and wellness appointments near you. 

BOOK APPOINTMENTS

Haircuts, massages, waxes, mani-pedis… or that new treatment you’ve been dying to try. Find expert salons & spas near you in seconds, and book your self-care fix whenever you fancy - anytime, anywhere.

WHY TREATWELL

Discover the best hairdressers, nail techs, and salons near you - your next favourite is just a tap away.
Filter thousands of salons, snag the best appointment, and book it there and then.
Read millions of honest reviews from real customers, and know what to expect before you even step inside.
Add appointments to your calendar in a few taps. Life’s busy - we’ll keep track.
Get to your appointment easily with our in-app map functionality.
Choose off-peak times (like afternoons or quiet periods) for a better price.
Pre-pay for your treatment, and breeze in and out on the day - smooth & stress-free.
Manage all your appointments in one place - rebook, reschedule, or cancel if plans change.
Reminders and deals straight to your phone - never miss an appointment, or a discount.


Treatwell is available across the UK, including London, Manchester, Birmingham, Glasgow, Liverpool, Edinburgh, Belfast, Leeds, Bristol, Sheffield, Newcastle - and across 13 European countries.

Quickly and easily connect and control your smart home devices through SmartThings.
SmartThings is compatible with 100s of smart home brands. So you can control all of your smart home gadgets in one place, including your Samsung Smart TV and smart home appliances.
With SmartThings, you can connect, monitor and control multiple smart home devices quicker and easier. Connect your Samsung smart TVs, smart appliances, smart speakers and brands like Ring, Nest and Philips Hue - all from one app.
Then control your smart devices using voice assistants including Google Assistant

[Key Features]
- Control and check in on your home from wherever you are
- Connect your smart devices across many different brands to work together by setting ‘scenes’
- Build routines that are set on time, weather, and device status, so your home runs smoothly in the background
- Allow shared control by giving access to other users
- Receive status updates about your devices with automated notifications
- Talk to your devices using Google Assistant
- Track, monitor and save money on energy with SmartThings Energy. See how much your home and compatible Samsung devices cost to run, and try various energy saving features, such as AI saving mode, or schedule devices to run during off peak hours.
- Receive recipe recommendations by scanning meal kits, wine, and meat. Plan, shop and prep meals with the help of SmartThings Cooking 

※ Some features may not be available in all countries.

[App requirements]
Some mobile devices may not be supported.
- iOS 16.0 or later / iPhone 6s or later / iPad mini 4 or later

-

MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.
With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

––––––––––––––––––––
If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. IKEA vizija yra kurti gražesnį kasdienį gyvenimą daugeliui žmonių. Štai kodėl sukūrėme šią programėlę – ja naudodamiesi, malonių patirčių galite susikurti ir patys.

Ieškokite ir atraskite
Net ir į prekių paiešką galima pažiūrėti kūrybiškai, todėl mūsų programėlėje ji superpaprasta. Čia rasite visas IKEA prekes su kainomis, galėsite apžiūrėti parduotuvės naujienas ir tikrai atrasite tai, ko reikia, kad namuose būtų gera!

Patiko? Išsisaugokite
Jei radote patinkančią prekę, bet kol kas neketinate įsigyti, išsisaugokite ją norų sąraše. Tai padaryti galite bet kurioje programėlės vietoje – tiek prekių, tiek įkvėpimo puslapiuose, o taip pat – nuskaitę prekės kodą parduotuvėje.

Pasisemkite įkvėpimo
Laikas pasisemti įkvėpimo ir skleisti idėjas! Turime daugybę įkvepiančių idėjų jūsų namams, tad ieškokite pagal kategoriją, pasižymėkite patikusias ir nepamirškite pasidalinti su kitais.

Apsipirkite neišeidami iš namų
Tereikia įdėti prekes į krepšelį, atsiskaityti ir laukti. Vos keli spustelėjimai ekrane, ir jūsų užsakytos prekės atkeliaus tiesiai į namus. Programėlėje galite išsisaugoti visus savo adresus, pasirinkti pristatymo dieną, laiką bei kainą.

Pasiruošę pradėti ir imtis kūrybos?

-	Set timers and schedules to automatically turn lights on or off.

Compatible with Dyson Solarcycle Morph™ desk and Dyson Solarcycle Morph™ floor.

More features

Get help

Be the first to find out

The following access permissions are necessary for the ThinQ app. 
All the access permissions requested are optional access permission, so even if you do not allow them, you can still use the app except for the related services. (Including OS Request Permissions such as "Siri & Search", "Notification", "Background App Refresh", and "Cellular Data")

[Optional Access Permissions]
• Location
- To find and connect to nearby Wi-Fi when registering the product.

- To search for and use information about current locations, such as weather.
- To check your current location in the "Smart Routines" function.

• Camera
- To take a profile picture

- To take and attach photos in "1:1 Inquiry."
- To record and store purchase receipts when registering additional information about the product..(미국 Only)

• Photo, Media, File

- To record and store purchase receipts when registering additional information about the product.
- To view photo/video on your smartphone on the TV.
- To use in “Chat with LG” to save photos/videos of product symptoms or proof of purchase
- To use in “Chat with LG” when entering the product and serial number information

• Media and Apple Music
- To view photo/video on your smartphone on the TV.

• Microphone
- To check product status via Smart Diagnosis
- To use in “Chat with LG” when inputting through the microphone in the input window and using STT.

• Local Network
- To obtain the device connecting Wi-Fi info when adding devices

• Bluetooth
- To find and connect to nearby Bluetooth devices when adding a product to the app.

• HomeKit
- To add IoT-based products

• Notifications
- Notifications are essential for receiving updates on product status, important notices, benefits, and information.

PURE is a dating app for curious people to show up in their most playful version of themselves. It’s a space to be honest with your intentions and clear in your boundaries.

Connect with like-minded community to create and explore new exciting experiences in a safe and supportive space.

Let your imagination go wild and get ready for amazing dates!

* HOW PURE WORKS?
Everything starts with Personal Ads. To see other people in the feed, you need to post your Ad. Write what kind of experience you are looking for and find someone who would share the same experience with you. Be creative and original with your ads, that's always appealing.

* IN PURE ALL BORDERS ARE OPEN
Paris, New-York or London? You can check any city worldwide and meet people from PURE community from around the globe.  

* WHAT HAPPENS IN PURE STAYS IN PURE
Photos self-destruct right after being seen, and in case someone takes a screenshot, you will get a notification about that. Also, all chat messages, including photos and audio, shared in chats cannot be saved to the phone's gallery.

* OUR MISSION IS TO KEEP PURE A PURE EXPERIENCE
Safety of our community is one of our key priorities. We are constantly improving our algorithms to find and get rid of scam and spam accounts, also our system sends automatic alerts on trigger words that might be used by scammers, so don't be surprised in case you will get a warning. 
Keep chatting anonymously via PURE and do not switch to other messengers. You know what they say: better safe than sorry. 

PURE uses auto-renewing subscriptions — you have to subscribe to get inside.
Here’s what you should know about PURE subscriptions:

- If you choose to purchase a weekly, monthly or annual subscription you will be able to go online and interact via chats with other users during the chosen subscription period. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change with a notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.
- All subscriptions renew automatically unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations.
- Auto-renewal can be canceled at any time by going to your settings in the Apple Store after the purchase.
- All personal data is handled under PURE’s privacy policy https://pure.app/content/en/privacy
- Terms and conditions: https://pure.app/terms/

The best secret santa generator app has arrived. You can now organize the gift exchange with your friends really easy and free. It's the best way to draw the names on christmas.

Create a new group entering the gift delivery date, the fixed budget and a message, like conditions or anything you want to tell your friends.

Invite all your friends and family to join. You can add the participants using their email or sharing the group code on WhatsApp, Facebook, Messenger, Instagram, email or SMS.

Add gifts to your wish list so your Secret Santa knows what would make you happiest.

Add the rules you want to prevent certain people giving away to others, e.g. couples, enemies, etc.

When they have joined, press the button and everyone will receive an email or a notification with the results. Now try to find the perfect gift for your friend!

Secret Santa is a random name generator for your Secret Santa events. Also known as Kris Kringle, draw names for your holiday Christmas parties at the office or among friends.
It is now easy to organise your gift exchange, create your group and wishlist.

Instead of scribbling down names and popping them out of a hat, use this very advanced technology to send emails or display a live draw.

It is very easy to create a new Secret Santa group with this app.

FEATURES:

◆ Online Secret Santa
Set up your Secret Santa gift exchange by creating a group, set a budget and date, add the names of friends, family and set exclusions. This app allows unlimited participants.
Secret Santa will then draw names and let you send invitations by email, text message, WhatsApp or any other messaging service.

◆ Exclude pairs
Easily set exclusions, selected participants will not be paired together.
This feature ensures that partners will not gift each other. You can also prevent draws from the previous year.

◆ Without registration
This Secret Santa app requires no registration. Only one device is necessary to organise the draw.

◆ Offline Secret Santa
The offline mode will set up your gift exchange on the spot, directly on the screen.

◆ Wishlist

Roborock App is a dedicated application designed to control Roborock’s smart hardware devices. 
It supports network-enabled products in Roborock’s robotic vacuum cleaners, wet and dry vacuum cleaners, and molecular sieve-based washer dryers.
You can remotely control smart devices and check their status and cleaning progress through this app anytime, anywhere.
Easily unlock more advanced features through the Roborock app.

【Roborock Robotic Vacuum Cleaner】
· Check the cleaning map and path anywhere and anytime you want, and control the cleaning progress in real-time. 
· Choose from various personalized cleaning methods, including room cleaning, zone cleaning, scheduled cleaning, and spot cleaning routines.
· Set up frequently used cleaning tasks as routines for one-tap starts. 
· Choose multiple cleaning preferences, including Vacuum, Mop, Vac & Mop, SmartPlan (applicable to certain models only), and Customize mode. 
· Set up a personalized cleaning plan by adjusting suction power, water flow, cleaning frequency, and route (applicable to certain models only).
· Enables you to edit a map based on your home and set names for thresholds, carpets, floor types, furniture, and rooms. 
· Set up invisible walls and no-go zones and your robot will not cross or enter them during cleaning.
· Enjoy a variety of fun features, including remote viewing, obstacle photos, pet snapshots, cruise mode, pet search, and custom tones (applicable to select models only).

【Roborock Wet and Dry Vacuum Cleaner】
· Adjust water flow, suction power, roller speed, and detergent level (applicable to select models only) based on the floor and dirt level.
· Smart scheduled self-cleaning and drying: automatically initiates self-cleaning and drying based on historical operation records.

【Roborock Washer Dryer】
· Check the washing progress and operating status anywhere and anytime you want.
· Choose from over 20 smart washing and drying programs to meet the professional needs of various fabrics and clothing, ensuring optimal washing performance.
· Set one program as the App Program for quick access on the control panel.

【Permissions】
To provide certain services, you need to enable the relevant permissions on your mobile device. We will only need the relevant permissions and access your personal information (if relevant) when you use the relevant functions. For the optional permissions, you can refuse or withdraw these permissions at any time, for which you may not be able to use the corresponding services, but this will not affect other functions of the App. The current permissions that the app may need are as follows: 
· Location (Optional)
Accesses location information to connect to WiFi, find nearby devices ready for connection, and retrieve details about the current WiFi connection.
· Camera (Optional)
Enables the camera to scan QR codes for easier WiFi connection.
· Photos (Optional)
Allows access to photos for uploading profile pictures and attaching images when providing feedback. If your device supports features like downloading obstacle images, taking screenshots, or recording during remote viewing, photos and videos can be stored.
· Microphone (Optional)
Used for sound transmission on devices that support remote viewing.
· WLAN (Optional)
Facilitates connection to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices for communication and connectivity.
· Bluetooth (Optional)
Enables connection to Bluetooth signals from smart devices for communication and device connecting.
· Notifications (Optional)
Allows the app to send you device and system notifications.
· Local Network (Optional)
When connecting devices on the iOS local network, grants access to the local network to connect to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices.
· Siri & Search (Optional)
When opening Siri on iOS, interacts with Siri to control the starting and moving of devices based on the Routines set up in the mobile device.
